{"tid":1140042,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 未有開腔護夫！傳洪欣收集證據大反擊","createTime":"2019-05-05T15:53:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T16:30:45.000Z","uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0b3b6ef054d4feca35c60b89faee77c26bcc9370","tid":1140042,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T15:53:11.000Z","msg":"洪欣老公張丹峰跟經理人畢瀅的出軌事件，張丹峰雖然已出聲明否認，但未得洪欣開腔撐夫，故事件沒完沒了。內地更有傳媒翻摷洪欣早年在一個清談節目中，透露為怕影響老公事業，兩人曾瞞婚3年，以表洪欣當年如何護夫。洪欣曾稱：「主要也是考慮到丹峰，因為他畢竟還是個新人，如果他跟一個比較有名的人結婚，會不會是給大家有些想法，來影響他事業的發展，等他事業愈來愈好了，然後再公開。」 <br />\n<br />\n不過，時至今天，出軌事件實在傷透她的心，故有內地傳媒爆料，指洪欣正與狗仔搜刮畢瀅和老公的料，而其子張鎬濂也在幫媽媽找證據。消息更指，一直保持沉默的洪欣，將證據收集完整之後，會放出來向張丹峰反擊，外間更為此擔心與張丹峰情同父子的張鎬濂，將會因這件「出軌事件」而反面收場。"},{"pid":"ff08c33a321fbba885082e0fc36a79ad91a08476","tid":1140042,"uid":52524,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T15:53:45.000Z","msg":"有預感會好撚嘈"},{"pid":"8cd586a080835d1097c434e54822046d53960eb8","tid":1140042,"uid":48905,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T15:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/trzfSUh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtrzfSUh.png&h=1ebcfec5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b58aa0d33f6911c0097b8b5e3a11e4790ca1951","tid":1140042,"uid":48905,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T15:54:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iQiDQF1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiQiDQF1.png&h=bfe7dab7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d45a162ba9dec3c3c99085f35bfc5d2b9ae7fd3","tid":1140042,"uid":48905,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T15:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VufnxUq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVufnxUq.png&h=285dd7f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e980003bf64e50749e07a0830982848e71466d88","tid":1140042,"uid":48905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T15:55:20.00